Enactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE REMISSION OF CERTAIN DEBTS OWED TO HER
MAJESTY IN RIGHT OF CANADA BY CERTAIN PROVINCES - which provides for the
remission of provincial debts to the Crown accumulated over the years 1959
to 1997, in the provision of humanitarian and disaster assistance.
